# Theming & Assets

- Use a centralized `ThemeData` and support light/dark/system via `ThemeMode`. Use `ColorScheme.fromSeed` for palettes
- Use `google_fonts` and a defined `TextTheme` for consistent fonts. Customize `appBarTheme`, `elevatedButtonTheme`, etc.
- Declare asset paths in `pubspec.yaml`. Use `Image.asset` for local assets
- For `Image.network`, always provide `loadingBuilder` and `errorBuilder` for better UX
- Prefer vibrant palettes and clear typography hierarchy (hero text, section headlines, list headlines)
